Package org.nlpub.watset.graph

Class MarkovClustering<V,​E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nlpub.watset.graph.MarkovClustering<V,​E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - vertices
    E - edges
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Clustering<V>
    public class MarkovClustering<V,​E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Clustering<V>
    This is an implementation of the Markov Clustering (MCL) algorithm. It assumes processing of relatively small graphs due to the lack of pruning optimizations.
    See Also:
    van Dongen (2008)
